Package: toddler
Title: Make Clean Data Dirty
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Scott", "Davis", email = "sadavis05@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions that allow you to add empty rows and columns to a data frame, stack data frames on top of each other, and format column names.  The resulting character data frame is nicely formatted for sharing.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: dplyr (>= 0.7.0), tidyr (>= 0.8.0), stringr (>= 1.4.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests:
    testthat
